"""In-spec deterministic self-healing layer (AUTO-GENERATED — do not edit by hand).

Vendors the byte-equivalent pure scorer from app/services/healing/ (confidence/geometry/
candidates) + the verbatim xpath JS from explorer/locators.py. Runs INSIDE the generated spec
subprocess on a locator miss: live candidate search -> deterministic blend -> HARD uniqueness
